Text: It's an iso file, so I guess you have to basically mount it with Daemon Tools or something.

ISO doesn't work, nor dos the installer file in it. Just drops a bunch of viruses, namely 'Application.Keylogger.PZL', 'Gen:Variant.MalDropper.1' and 'Adware.LoudMo.A'.

Don't waste your time with this torrent.

The only thing I seem to be missing is a serial, since the installer asks for one? There's another folder:
ViTALiTY with 2 subfolders with .exe and .dll files - not very useful afaik.. Also a bunch of hidden files, but no clues as how to make this run.
